               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was not near the shop—I was going down a turning to<lb></lb>wards Kennington Common—I saw them on the ground—he asked me what I had got—I said, nothing belonging to him—he said yes, I had a pair of green trowsers, and at the station-house he said it was a pair of drab trowsers.</p>
